Robert Goodman is a former UCDavis student who attended the institution from 2002 to 2005. He subsequentially graduated in fall 2005. He is notedly known for his career as Social Chairman at the Chi Phi Fraternity Organization in 2004. During this time several Social events converged under his leadership, some including Beer Baseball, Fall Quarter After School Bash, Sloshball, and a variety of other activities. He is also well known more recently for his involvement in the wrestling theme social events at private bashes.
